 Proto1000 woke up from his dark sleep. He returned to his solid form takeing 
shape as a regular look a like to the bot Magmatron in his robot mode. He 
walked to the top of the mountain. He scanned the area. He found the 
decepticon  signal and sent a message."My name is proto1000 I am searching 
for a faction to go under.  I am interested in joining your group. If you 
will send someone to meet me here so I may discuss my possible following."

--part1_83.e79953c.28a984a5_boundary
